sequenceDiagram
  participant Caller
  participant Retell
  participant API
  participant DB
  participant PMS
  Caller->>Retell: "Anything Thursday morning?"
  Retell->>API: search_availability
  API->>DB: availability windows + active appointments
  DB-->>API: live slots
  API-->>Retell: speakable options
  Caller->>Retell: confirms slot and name
  Retell->>API: book_appointment(idempotencyKey)
  API->>DB: transaction conflict check + insert
  DB-->>API: confirmed appointment
  API->>PMS: idempotent write-back
  PMS-->>API: external PMS ID
  API-->>Retell: confirmed doctor, branch, date, time
